  <summary>Your proofreading assistant</summary>
  <translation type="gettext">re.sonny.Eloquent</translation>
  <description>
    <p>Eloquent is a proofreading software for English, Spanish, French, German, Portuguese, Polish, Dutch, and more than 20 other languages. It finds many errors that a simple spell checker cannot detect.</p>
    <p>It works fully offline, powered by LanguageTool standalone server.</p>
  </description>
